{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bf8a6ced88","title":"给周文楠的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"913db34a16","index":0,"year":1950,"month":5,"day":12,"articleId":"bf8a6ced88"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/28-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji28":{"comments":[{"id":"5666862326","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"bf8a6ced88","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"周文楠，原是毛泽东之弟毛泽单的夫人。当时任沈阳市人民法院刑事庭庭长。"},{"id":"0f23132f5b","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"bf8a6ced88","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指周陈轩写给女儿周文楠的信。信中叙述了她自己在湖南韶山一人生活，无人照顾等情况。"}],"contents":[{"id":"c7a0770cac","type":"title","text":"给周文楠的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"bf8a6ced88"},{"id":"5666862326","type":"paragraph","text":"文楠同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"bf8a6ced88"},{"id":"0f23132f5b","type":"paragraph","text":"来信收到，甚感。接你母亲去东北和你一道生活一事，我认为是好的。我可以写信给湖南方面发给旅费。惟你母年高，一人在路上无人招扶是否安全，是否需要你自己去湖南接她同去东北方为妥当，请你考虑告我。如你自己去接，我给湖南的信即由你带去。附件还你。江青她们都好。祝你健康","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"bf8a6ced88"},{"id":"00d9b4a266","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"bf8a6ced88"},{"id":"202924080c","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五O、五月十二日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"bf8a6ced88"}],"page":{"id":"40d2906880","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"bf8a6ced88","start":378,"end":378}}}},"__N_SSG":true}